Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway discuss Dan's uncanny ability to pick baseball games as Ross forces him to choose today's games and updated series. Ross calls out the listener who he made the "Russell Wilson Bet" with and gloats over his half point victory and how the Seattle Seahawks never cover.
